## Summary

This document provides an evidence-based summary of the current documented state of **The Divan and the Sword (TDS)** immediately prior to its first official public release (**v1.0.1**).

As of **2026-07-09**, the project is in the **Pre-DOI** phase. The repository structure, core documentation, website configuration, release documentation, and citation metadata have been prepared for the first public release. According to the documented repository state, these materials have been committed to the repository. However, the project's publication process is not yet complete because the first GitHub Release has not been published and a Zenodo DOI has not yet been assigned.

This handover summary is intended to support project continuity by documenting the current state of the project, identifying the remaining publication milestones, and providing a clear operational roadmap for the transition from the **Pre-DOI** phase to the **Post-DOI** phase.

Throughout the project, all status statements are governed by the principles of **Evidence Before Status** and **Traceability**. Project status may be updated only when supported by verifiable evidence. The GitHub repository, Git commit history, GitHub Releases, GitHub Pages, and Zenodo records constitute the authoritative sources for determining the official status of the project.

This document is a coordination and transition record. It summarizes the project's documented state as of **2026-07-09**, supports continuity between project phases, and does not replace the repository or official publication records. Any future revisions to this document should be based solely on verifiable evidence obtained from the project's authoritative records.
